#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This page details how to configure your [[hardware]] for operation in the "
"mesh."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "General instructions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Those instructions attempt to be platform-independent or at least cover "
"multiple platforms. This 4 step process should get you on the mesh, with "
"full internet access if you are so privileged."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"[[configuration/flashing]] - flashing your device with the proper firmware "
"(optional - if you already have the software on your machine, just go to "
"step 2)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
msgid ""
"[[configuration/ad-hoc]] - basic point to point configuration, includes "
"[[adress allocation]]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '3. '
msgid "[[configuration/olsrd]] - configuring OLSRd to join the mesh"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '4. '
msgid ""
"[[configuration/vpn]] - configuring OpenVPN to be able to access the "
"gateways to the real internet"
msgstr ""

