#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Network topology"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We need to decide of a topology. Opennet has an interesting concept, where "
"public IPs are hidden behind VPN gateways:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "<https://wiki.opennet-initiative.de/w/images/3/3d/Opennet-Struktur-VPNGateways.png>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "This has a few advantages:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: ' 1. '
msgid "strong over-the-air encryption"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: ' 2. '
msgid "no need to change gateway if network topology changes"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: ' 3. '
msgid "access to the internet only to subscribers"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "We are also considering ad-hoc mode and OLSR, see [[todo/network_topology]]."
msgstr ""

